{"tid":423943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲廢老咁撚捱得","createTime":"2017-10-04T10:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T08:10:38.000Z","uid":55851,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"057d80eca40c7d1f75e5dc240a4bd6f43ce24c09","tid":423943,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"點解個個都可以捱撚到6,70歲未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時又煙又酒，食野一係飲茶一係大家樂大快活，冇營養又高油鹽糖到仆街。<br />\n唔做運動，大肚腩又周身骨痛，又唔沖涼成身皮膚病，仲要平時極度污糟惹唔少病毒細菌。<br />\n<br />\n但係就偏偏好撚長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 霸撚住啲公屋同福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e418cb88a64fdcaf62d076114b8fe25d661b24","tid":423943,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"這是經過黨的磨練後所得的成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60fa4ad346fde86d2f7cdc63920541d23fe0d7a","tid":423943,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f808bb80bd47b0d93342176389f59496a3c38be","tid":423943,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"最撚憎班死廢老隨地吐痰"},{"pid":"024be6be6e49f1f7a111acc9c2c72ae9c9a1e2c5","tid":423943,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20d14b98963e46780655ce49788819eab87d1bc6","tid":423943,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"所以唔需要讓座畀班老嘢<br />\n更加唔應該搞全民退休保障<br />\n我番工啲錢唔係用嚟養人哋老竇老母😒"},{"pid":"d7e246b890e3da2c55627e535fabcc45af580641","tid":423943,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你覺得食咩先有營養?</blockquote><br />\nM記？"},{"pid":"d2a48732b31995aa48e2d139416997790f45aaca","tid":423943,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score